javmos.components

Class JavmosPanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • javmos.components.JavmosPanel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class JavmosPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    This class creates a custom JPanel that renders the GUI's Cartesian Plane, function and calculates its significant point(s). You cannot add any other methods nor modify the method signatures.
